lead_paragraph: Hyun Soo Kim hit his fifth home run, a two-run shot in the second inning, and the Baltimore Orioles completed a three-game sweep of the Arizona Diamondbacks with a 2-1 victory Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Kim's Two-Run Homer Leads Orioles Past Diamondbacks, 2-1
